#- New Xiphias Ordinance
as of November 1st, 2013 (and retroactively nullifying sections of Government Charter 1).
         Bill #2
As of the declaration of this bill, former Chairman TrampyCrabCake officially resigns
#- from his position, and appoints a new Chairman, AvaloKitesvara. This selection is voted a unanimous "Yea," by the other 2 members of the council, Mr__Wiggles and firedart118. 
